  92:Middlewares/Third_Party/SubGHz_Phy/radio_driver/radio.c **** /**
  93:Middlewares/Third_Party/SubGHz_Phy/radio_driver/radio.c ****   * \brief Calculates rounding division of ( X / N )
  94:Middlewares/Third_Party/SubGHz_Phy/radio_driver/radio.c ****   *
  95:Middlewares/Third_Party/SubGHz_Phy/radio_driver/radio.c ****   * \param [in] X numerator
